|2 |  NESTED-LOOP OUTER JOIN      |        |3842385  |15467134759|
|3 |   PX PARTITION ITERATOR      |        |200000   |128131     |
|4 |    TABLE SCAN                |t1      |200000   |128131     |
|5 |   MATERIAL                   |        |200000   |266781     |
